{"tid":627612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【知法犯法】兩警掃黃拉妓女 順手牽羊偷錢被捕","createTime":"2018-04-13T06:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T07:37:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e56de3b30c67445f96d9bb9217105ff259c26112","tid":627612,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180413/58067707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58067707&d=95vaTXnWF%2BaQOTHEBviKW%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a99ddd1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58067707&h=c4c57b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180413/58067707</a><br />\n<br />\n 警隊懷疑有人監守自盜，兩名警員涉嫌在掃黃行動中偷妓女錢被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，警方東區特別職務隊人員，本周初進行一項掃黃行動，拘捕多名涉嫌賣淫女子。警員將被捕女子帶返警署調查期間，懷疑有人順手牽羊，偷去妓女銀包內3000元，稍後警員替她們進行俗稱「打包頭」的程序，即將她們身上的物件放入袋內收起，有妓女發現銀包內的3000元不翼而飛，即時向警員舉報。<br />\n<br />\n警方翻看cctv，拍下有人偷竊，事後拘捕涉案兩名特別職務隊警員，案件已港島總區重案組跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一次過2球"},{"pid":"3f8f9e297fdf30088a184fd8c9ada4aeebe57cae","tid":627612,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4c40fb40e2af3d3cd933269c93a5c575d32d79","tid":627612,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"隔離班手足立大功啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次過2單"},{"pid":"cb4975cbafec730f8b3b20ca0f7d6318dac285ae","tid":627612,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56de3b30c67445f96d9bb9217105ff259c26112","tid":627612,"uid":51